@startuml spikecodes_stotra

actor User

cloud "AWS" {
  rectangle "AWS Amplify" as Amplify {
    component "React Frontend" as Frontend
  }
  
  rectangle "Elastic Cloud Compute (EC2)" as EC2 {
    component "Node.js/Express Backend" as Backend
  }
  
  database "MongoDB Atlas" as MongoDB
}

cloud "External Services" {
  [Yahoo Finance API]
  [Alpha Vantage API]
  [NewsFilter API]
}

User -> Frontend : Interacts with

Frontend -> Amplify : Deploys to
Frontend <-> Backend : API Requests/Responses

Backend -> EC2 : Runs on
Backend <-> MongoDB : Reads/Writes data

Backend <-> [Yahoo Finance API] : Fetches stock data
Backend <-> [Alpha Vantage API] : Fetches financial data
Backend <-> [NewsFilter API] : Fetches news

@enduml